OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont legal advice over
OL,4,C'controversial' Irish language signs
OL,6,FUTV has seen correspondence between
OL,7,Fthe Communities minister Gordon Lyons
OL,8,Fand the Infrastructure minister Liz
OL,9,FKimmins which shows government
OL,10,Fsolicitors believe introducing Irish
OL,11,Flanguage signage at Grand Central
OL,12,FStation in Belfast is a cross-cutting
OL,13,Fand controversial decision, which
OL,14,Fshould have been referred to the
OL,15,FExecutive.
OL,17,FBack in March new-in-post
OL,18,FInfrastructure minister Liz Kimmins
OL,19,Fannounced she was to introduce Irish
OL,20,FLanguage signage at Grand Central
OL,21,FStation at a cost of #150,000.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
