OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont legal advice over
OL,4,C'controversial' Irish language signs
OL,6,FDUP ministers reacted furiously to the
OL,7,Fannouncement, insisting the matter was
OL,8,Fcontroversial and cross-cutting - ie.
OL,9,Fits impact cuts across two or more
OL,10,Fgovernment departments.
OL,12,FIn those circumstances, Stormont
OL,13,Fministers are required to bring matter
OL,14,Fto the Executive for agreement from
OL,15,Fother ministers.
OL,17,FWhen the matter was discussed at the
OL,18,FExecutive days later, the deputy First
OL,19,FMinister Emma Little Pengelly branded
OL,20,Fthe move "utterly shambolic".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
