OL,6,FAt the time she told the post-meeting
OL,7,Fpress conference: "I reaffirmed our
OL,8,Fclear view that this issue is
OL,9,Fcontroversial. Therefore it should
OL,10,Fhave been brought to the Executive
OL,11,FCommittee for agreement. We will be
OL,12,Fseeking additional information and
OL,13,Fconsidering the way forward."
OL,15,FShe added: "All controversial,
OL,16,Fsignificant or cross-cutting matters
OL,17,Fdo have that legal responsibility in
OL,18,Fterms of ministers bringing that to
OL,19,Fthe Executive."
