OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont legal advice over
OL,4,C'controversial' Irish language signs
OL,6,FBut it didn't end there. Loyalist
OL,7,Factivist Jamie Bryson announced he was
OL,8,Flaunching a legal challenge to the
OL,9,Fdecision.
OL,11,FUTV later revealed the Communities
OL,12,Fminister Gordon Lyons had also decided
OL,13,Fto legally challenge the move and so
OL,14,Fhad intervened in the Bryson case.
OL,16,FNow UTV has seen correspondence which
OL,17,Freveals Liz Kimmins and Gordon Lyons
OL,18,Fwere at odds from the moment the
OL,19,Fannouncement was made.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
