OL,6,FIn no less than seven letters,
OL,7,Fexchanged between March and and June,
OL,8,Fthe two ministers disagreed over
OL,9,Fwhether the decision was cross cutting
OL,10,Fand controversial.
OL,12,FFinally on 28th May the Communities
OL,13,Fminister wrote to his Infrastructure
OL,14,Fcounterpart saying he had received
OL,15,Flegal advice from the Departmental
OL,16,FSolicitor's Office.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
