OL,6,FHe writes: "That advice confirms that
OL,7,Fyour decision meets the test for
OL,8,F'controversial' and 'cross cutting'
OL,9,Fand should have been referred to the
OL,10,FExecutive for discussion and agreement
OL,11,Fprior to being made."
OL,13,FHe again urges Mrs Kimmins to bring
OL,14,Fthe matter to the Executive for
OL,15,Fdiscussion.
