OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont legal advice over
OL,4,C'controversial' Irish language signs
OL,6,FWhen UTV asked Mrs Kimmins about the
OL,7,Fcorrespondence the minister stuck to
OL,8,Fher position.
OL,10,FShe said: "I wasn't advised to go to
OL,11,Fthe Executive but I am confident, and
OL,12,Fstill am confident, that it didn't
OL,13,Fneed to happen. However as there are
OL,14,Flegal proceedings and the minister for
OL,15,FCommunities has joined the legal
OL,16,Fproceedings I think that's all I can
OL,17,Freally say at this stage as it is now
OL,18,Fin the hands of the court."
