OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont legal advice over
OL,4,C'controversial' Irish language signs
OL,6,FIf the court finds in favour of the
OL,7,FInfrastructure minister the work to
OL,8,Fintroduce Irish language signage will
OL,9,Fgo ahead unimpeded.
OL,11,FHowever, if the matter is resolved in
OL,12,Ffavour of Mr Bryson and the
OL,13,FCommunities minister, the
OL,14,FInfrastructure minister will come
OL,15,Funder considerable pressure to bring
OL,16,Fto matter to the Executive for
OL,17,Fagreement.
OL,19,FThe High Court hearing is due to take
OL,20,Fplace on September 25th.
